{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"35":"Interpretation of Dreams"},"section_detail":{"35":{"hadithnumber_first":3893,"hadithnumber_last":3926,"arabicnumber_first":3893,"arabicnumber_last":3926}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3900,"arabicnumber":3900,"text":"Rapporté par ‘Abdullah : Le Prophète (ﷺ) a dit : « Celui qui me voit en rêve m’a réellement vu, car le diable ne peut pas prendre mon apparence. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":35,"hadith":8}}]}